{"tid":1893880,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工應該睇份糧定興趣","createTime":"2020-02-23T14:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T12:24:05.000Z","uid":140675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"73c6560fc6d46b53002fdc69a53da4612a5873d9","tid":1893880,"uid":140675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"本身返緊parttime/freelance <br />\n但呢排肺炎cut咗好多甚至停咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變咗好得閒但又好想搵錢同搵嘢忙下<br />\n<br />\n咁啱見到份pt係幫手搞下小型event同workshop<br />\n睇過吓間嘢都搞過唔同藝術類型嘅workshop <br />\n都幾有興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢個先係重點 <br />\n佢話人工$45 per hr起跳 $45真係太cheap <br />\n閒閒地返開promoter都至少佢double<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但勝在如果返呢間有機會接觸到自己有興趣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣問題其實我都成日思考緊<br />\n如果grad咗唔睇人工唔做返個行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉做自己有興趣想試嘅嘢（但有可能人地心諗你都On9讀咁耐畢業唔做返本行）係咪真係on9？<br />\n呢個問題我問過身邊人好耐 10個有8個都係叫我現實啲做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港地都係好現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1892e74342059624775e71907e819a560cffa311","tid":1893880,"uid":37869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"睇你自己<br />\n唔知足的人揀左搵錢就會後悔冇揀興趣<br />\n揀左興趣就後悔冇揀搵錢"},{"pid":"b6605b6c47dfe0a2daf10764419d5fb500f0aa7b","tid":1893880,"uid":103248,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"有家底&gt;興趣<br />\n無家底&gt;睇錢"},{"pid":"a72385bd5737a627fb36284ce7d62ddf26a59546","tid":1893880,"uid":289751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"好現實咁問返你<br />\n等唔等錢開飯?<br />\n唔等既咪去馬囉"},{"pid":"be90f260b87bae7b7c9df748b7b0caa875973e1e","tid":1893880,"uid":161467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e981fde0e92914f7e354384c25bf5d6629b8cd9","tid":1893880,"uid":301839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"屌你pt 好撚但啦"},{"pid":"24ba7d14a36163bb70fade3f6f239ce67f0af4a3","tid":1893880,"uid":197317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e981fde0e92914f7e354384c25bf5d6629b8cd9","tid":1893880,"uid":301839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"屌你pt 好撚但啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"啱呀 煙腸冇錢都照返㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4f2f4f277dcb4d589ec212a2b90ff2bbcc97ed","tid":1893880,"uid":63952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"睇份糧，興趣嘅嘢多數收工後Develop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928cc7aa47a51602191f833fa23ab4f4082a8863","tid":1893880,"uid":52194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"有錢有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e30eb471f277219d14f15ed41573f281a43e53","tid":1893880,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"大聲啲對鏡講 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返工為啲咩</span>"},{"pid":"8fa329a275d268badef741370a547f20df598333","tid":1893880,"uid":237300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"如果份糧生活到就興趣，因為咁樣你24小時都會做自己鍾意做嘅嘢，人生都係想咁姐，但如果份糧養自己都唔掂就唔該每日拎返8-10個鐘出嚟搵錢再係工餘時間講興趣"},{"pid":"a01052bc2be2d44a387936f2183649392cb8b5e8","tid":1893880,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"eec20faa831098e50444e1fc19655ce2edb12242","tid":1893880,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"$$"},{"pid":"b7ef4fcf8ffec7a34052d6a96e0a62d971e5b50c","tid":1893880,"uid":295511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"你番緊工定興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac29bf88573457e4e3c7a22ea32c1c4367e5cfe","tid":1893880,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"出黎做full time幾年你就唔會再講興趣"},{"pid":"653a85f5b91a5d34a3bc4f82a5fb2a1f884c8649","tid":1893880,"uid":274722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"少年，你太年輕了，你以為你人生可以真心講我真係好鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0052c9dfa2f80ce70ebf95451f84c50eea6e846e","tid":1893880,"uid":266998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T20:42:55.000Z","msg":"pt姐 又唔係人生目標<br />\n試吓無妨嘅 反正你都冇野做<br />\n<br />\nbtw 咩promoter咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a57c0cf595d87cf7fcd0521e0d7d07565e5821","tid":1893880,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"慘得過份糧低兼唔係興趣<br />\n你有得選擇都好,好多都無得揀"},{"pid":"b660d72a0d2c21cd6241298a661b57a38c9da9bb","tid":1893880,"uid":140675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0052c9dfa2f80ce70ebf95451f84c50eea6e846e","tid":1893880,"uid":266998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T20:42:55.000Z","msg":"pt姐 又唔係人生目標<br />\n試吓無妨嘅 反正你都冇野做<br />\n<br />\nbtw 咩promoter咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"多數都係派吓啲新產品呀叫人like fb個啲姐"},{"pid":"b3e45b203183bc21c4c2b01ff9031f79026bc573","tid":1893880,"uid":140675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1892e74342059624775e71907e819a560cffa311","tid":1893880,"uid":37869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"